"title": "8421: equipping, physical",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8421: equipping, physical",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture provides illustrations of situations in which people are equipped to carry out physical actions.</p>\n<h2>Manual workers are equipped for their tasks</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:13-1Kgs5:14\">1KI 5:13–5:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:22\">GEN 4:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:3\">GEN 11:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:15\">GEN 24:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:1-Exod25:9\">EXO 25:1–25:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:10\">1KI 5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:21\">1KI 19:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra1:5-Ezra1:6\">EZR 1:5–1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:7-Neh2:8\">NEH 2:7–2:8</a></p>\n<h2>Musicians are equipped to play</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:29\">ISA 30:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:21\">GEN 4:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:4\">JOS 6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:16-1Sam16:18\">1SA 16:16–16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr25:6-1Chr25:7\">1CH 25:6–25:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps150:3-Ps150:5\">PSA 150:3–150:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:8\">REV 5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:2\">REV 15:2</a></p>\n<h2>Travellers are equipped for their journeys</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:4\">2SA 12:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:25\">GEN 42:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:19-Gen45:23\">GEN 45:19–45:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:7\">NEH 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:2\">JER 9:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:6\">LUK 11:6</a></p>\n<h2>Those equipped with signs of authority</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:42\">GEN 41:42</a> <em>Joseph</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:10\">GEN 49:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:17\">EXO 4:17</a> <em>Moses</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:10\">EST 3:10</a> <em>Haman</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:11\">EST 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth5:2\">EST 5:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:19\">MAT 16:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:2\">ACT 9:2</a></p>\n<h2>Equipping for burial</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen23:8-Gen23:9\">GEN 23:8–23:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:8\">MRK 14:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:56\">LUK 23:56</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:38-John19:42\">JHN 19:38–19:42</a></p>\n<h2>Soldiers are equipped for battle</h2>\n<h3>Israel's armies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:18\">EXO 13:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:5\">NUM 31:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:20-Num32:22\">NUM 32:20–32:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh4:13\">JOS 4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:8\">JOS 6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:16\">JDG 7:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:36-1Sam17:39\">1SA 17:36–17:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:26\">1KI 4:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:2\">1CH 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr14:8\">2CH 14:8</a></p>\n<h3>David</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:40\">1SA 17:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:9-1Sam22:10\">1SA 22:9–22:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:40\">2SA 22:40</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:39\">PSA 18:39</a></p>\n<h3>Israel's enemies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:6-Exod14:7\">EXO 14:6–14:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:5-1Sam17:7\">1SA 17:5–17:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:16\">2SA 21:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:23\">JER 6:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:4\">JER 46:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:42\">JER 50:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:13\">DAN 11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:47\">MAT 26:47</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:43\">MRK 14:43</a></p>\n<h2>Those providing protection are equipped</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:16-Neh4:18\">NEH 4:16–4:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:23-Acts23:25\">ACT 23:23–23:25</a></p>",
